00:18:53,333 --> 00:18:54,625
so we had to change things.

493
00:18:54,708 --> 00:18:57,416
From now on, Hana will
assist my role as overseer.

494
00:18:57,500 --> 00:18:58,625
Reporting for duty,

495
00:18:58,708 --> 00:19:00,250
by Executive Order
of the President!

496
00:19:00,333 --> 00:19:01,291
[KIYOSHI]
She's pretty cute.

497
00:19:01,375 --> 00:19:02,250
[GAKUTO]
A flowery maiden.

498
00:19:02,333 --> 00:19:03,416
[ANDRE]
I'd lick that.

499
00:19:03,500 --> 00:19:05,000
Okay, today we're
going to have some fun!

500
00:19:05,083 --> 00:19:06,458
It's a four leaf clover hunt!

501
00:19:06,541 --> 00:19:07,958
Let's go! [giggles]

502
00:19:08,041 --> 00:19:10,375
We'll press them and put them
into adorable bookmarks.

503
00:19:10,458 --> 00:19:11,791
Then we'll sell them
at the school fair

504
00:19:11,875 --> 00:19:14,000
and donate the money
to underprivileged kids!

505
00:19:14,083 --> 00:19:17,375
 ♪ Little four-leaf clover,
