506
00:19:17,458 --> 00:19:19,208
[KIYOSHI]
♪ I like the new girl. ♪

507
00:19:19,291 --> 00:19:20,458
She's all right,

508
00:19:20,541 --> 00:19:22,416
but I like what's over
there a whole lot more.

509
00:19:25,083 --> 00:19:26,541
[GAKUTO gasps]

510
00:19:26,625 --> 00:19:28,333
Indeed, the land
of milk and honey!

511
00:19:28,416 --> 00:19:31,416
Exactly, and they're way spicier
than the cold tamale we got now.

512
00:19:31,500 --> 00:19:33,625
[HANA] Oh hey, what are
you guys talking about?

513
00:19:33,708 --> 00:19:34,958
Any luck with those clovers?

514
00:19:35,041 --> 00:19:37,208
Yeah, yeah, yeah.
We're lookin', Toots.

515
00:19:37,291 --> 00:19:38,208
Huh?

516
00:19:38,291 --> 00:19:39,708
[SHINGO]
Eh?

517
00:19:39,791 --> 00:19:41,375
[HANA] Don't you ever patronize
me, you pathetic wannabe!

518
00:19:41,458 --> 00:19:43,791
[BOYS scream]

519
00:19:43,875 --> 00:19:46,250
I forgot to say Hana is
rated in the top four

520
00:19:46,333 --> 00:19:48,041
of her inter-high
school karate league.

521
00:19:48,125 --> 00:19:49,583
--It's true!
--[BOYS] Ma'am!

522
00:19:49,666 --> 00:19:50,916
[STUDENT 1D]
So the prison really exists?

523
00:19:51,000 --> 00:19:52,125
I thought it was a rumor.

524
00:19:52,208 --> 00:19:54,291
I'm glad! Those boys
got what they deserved.

525
00:19:54,375 --> 00:19:56,666
I don't understand why
they don't just expel them.

526
00:19:56,750 --> 00:19:59,583
No one who likes sumo...
can be all bad.

527
00:19:59,666 --> 00:20:01,791
--[gasps] Did you say something?
--[CHIYO] Mm...

528
00:20:01,875 --> 00:20:03,125
--[BOYS panting]
--[JOE coughing]

529
00:20:03,208 --> 00:20:05,083
[HANA] Wow! You sure
collected a lot of clovers!

530
00:20:05,166 --> 00:20:06,083
Good work, boys.

531
00:20:06,166 --> 00:20:07,833
What's this? A
three-leaf clover?

532
00:20:07,916 --> 00:20:09,708
You simpletons wanna try
to explain this to me?!

533
00:20:09,791 --> 00:20:11,041
[ANDRE]
Her beatings suck.

534
00:20:11,125 --> 00:20:12,625
[GAKUTO] I'm just not in
to that kind of violence.

535
00:20:12,708 --> 00:20:13,916
[SHINGO]
She's no fun at all.

536
00:20:14,000 --> 00:20:15,125
[JOE coughs]
...not fair!

537
00:20:15,208 --> 00:20:16,500
[KIYOSHI]
And why...?!

538
00:20:16,583 --> 00:20:18,916
Why is she wearing those
lame jorts under her skirt?!

539
00:20:19,000 --> 00:20:20,541
We can't even hope for
a glimpse of panty

540
00:20:20,625 --> 00:20:21,791
while we're being stomped!

541
00:20:21,875 --> 00:20:23,583
Now, go look again,
but do better!

542
00:20:23,666 --> 00:20:25,041
[BOYS]
Yes, ma'am!

543
00:20:25,125 --> 00:20:27,041
[MEIKO] I can't say I care
very much for the flavor

544
00:20:27,125 --> 00:20:28,375
of this herbal tea.

545
00:20:28,458 --> 00:20:30,583
How rude! That's my own
personal "original blend"!

546
00:20:30,666 --> 00:20:32,708
Things with Meiko were better.

547
00:20:34,000 --> 00:20:35,958
I'm gonna go look over there.

548
00:20:37,583 --> 00:20:39,250
--[squawk]
--[KIYOSHI gasps]

549
00:20:52,916 --> 00:20:54,166
[sighs]

550
00:20:54,250 --> 00:20:55,541
[CHIYO]
I knew it!

551
00:20:55,625 --> 00:20:58,375
No one who likes sumo
can be all bad.

552
00:21:00,625 --> 00:21:03,125
[KIYOSHI] I still haven't
apologized for the peeping.

553
00:21:03,208 --> 00:21:05,291
She probably hates me already.

554
00:21:05,375 --> 00:21:08,250
But if I just come clean,
maybe she'll forgive me.

555
00:21:08,333 --> 00:21:09,291
--Hi, Chiyo--
--[CHIYO] You didn't do

556
00:21:09,375 --> 00:21:12,375
what they said.
You wouldn't peep.

557
00:21:12,458 --> 00:21:14,541
You're too sweet for
something like that.

558
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:19,125
I knew it!

559
00:21:19,208 --> 00:21:20,416
[SHINGO]
We're freakin' dead.

560
00:21:20,500 --> 00:21:22,208
After all our
searching, this is it.

561
00:21:22,291 --> 00:21:24,916
That Hana chick is gonna crush
our skulls into a fine powder!

562
00:21:25,000 --> 00:21:26,458
Not just yet.

563
00:21:26,541 --> 00:21:28,416
There may still be a chance
of escaping the wrathful fury

564
00:21:28,500 --> 00:21:30,166
of the psychopathic
chick in bad jorts.

565
00:21:30,250 --> 00:21:31,000
You think so?

566
00:21:31,083 --> 00:21:32,833
What? You only found one?

567
00:21:32,916 --> 00:21:33,916
Do you want to die?

568
00:21:34,000 --> 00:21:35,291
Madam Hana...

569
00:21:35,375 --> 00:21:37,458
Were you aware that each
of the clover's four leaves

570
00:21:37,541 --> 00:21:39,583
has a distinct and
symbolic meaning?

571
00:21:39,666 --> 00:21:40,458
[HANA gasps]

572
00:21:40,541 --> 00:21:41,250
Uh... Like hope.

573
00:21:41,333 --> 00:21:42,166
Integrity.

574
00:21:42,250 --> 00:21:43,166
Fortune.

575
00:21:43,250 --> 00:21:45,375
The last... represents love.

576
00:21:45,458 --> 00:21:48,041
In other words, we are
a four-leaf clover!

577
00:21:48,125 --> 00:21:49,541
Meaning when you strike us,

578
00:21:49,625 --> 00:21:51,541
you're trampling on a pristine
field of dew-laden green--

579
00:21:51,625 --> 00:21:53,250
[HANA]
This allegory is heavy-handed!

580
00:21:53,333 --> 00:21:55,583
Besides, none of you scumbags
would make a good luck charm.

581
00:21:55,666 --> 00:21:57,375
You! What happened
to the other one?!

582
00:21:57,458 --> 00:21:59,750
He went searching for more
clovers all on his own.

583
00:21:59,833 --> 00:22:01,250
[CHIYO]
My grandma used to say,

584
00:22:01,333 --> 00:22:03,833
"No one who likes sumo
wrestling can be bad."

585
00:22:03,916 --> 00:22:05,208
I think she was on to something.

586
00:22:05,291 --> 00:22:06,750
After all...

587
00:22:06,833 --> 00:22:10,541
The kind of person who'd help
a baby bird is not a peeper.

588
00:22:10,625 --> 00:22:11,750
[KIYOSHI]
Out with it!

589
00:22:11,833 --> 00:22:13,583
You have to tell her now
or else later on...

590
00:22:13,666 --> 00:22:16,000
[CHIYO]
That sumo match we talked about?

591
00:22:16,083 --> 00:22:18,541
You can't go for
a while, I guess.

592
00:22:18,625 --> 00:22:21,583
Ah! Someone's coming!
I'll see you later!

593
00:22:21,666 --> 00:22:22,958
[KIYOSHI sighs]

594
00:22:23,041 --> 00:22:24,916
[KIYOSHI] Just tell her the
truth, you stupid idiot!

595
00:22:25,000 --> 00:22:26,500
[KIYOSHI]
Hey, Chiyo!

596
00:22:26,583 --> 00:22:27,708
[CHIYO]
Huh?

597
00:22:28,708 --> 00:22:30,666
I give you my word!

598
00:22:30,750 --> 00:22:32,208
We'll watch sumo soon!

599
00:22:32,291 --> 00:22:34,375
[KIYOSHI] Way to screw
everything up, mouth!

600
00:22:34,458 --> 00:22:35,958
I was going to confess to her,

601
00:22:36,041 --> 00:22:37,791
but now I'm making
promises I can't keep!

602
00:22:37,875 --> 00:22:39,625
[CHIYO chuckles]

603
00:22:41,416 --> 00:22:43,833
[KIYOSHI] And there goes
my chance to be decent.

604
00:22:43,916 --> 00:22:46,208
[HANA whimpers]

605
00:22:46,291 --> 00:22:47,083
[KIYOSHI]
Oh dammit!

606
00:22:47,166 --> 00:22:48,958
Is she here looking for me?!

607
00:22:49,041 --> 00:22:51,958
[HANA] It's no use!
I just can't hold it!

608
00:22:52,041 --> 00:22:53,250
[KIYOSHI gasps]

609
00:22:55,666 --> 00:22:57,625
Guess I drank too
much dandelion tea.

610
00:22:57,708 --> 00:22:59,458
[KIYOSHI] If she catches me
watching her, I'm dead!

611
00:22:59,541 --> 00:23:02,000
--[CROW caws]
--[KIYOSHI gasps]

612
00:24:42,708 --> 00:24:44,666
[KIYOSHI]
